The,Vibration,API,is,a,simple,browser,based,device,API,documented,by,the,W,C,Device,APIs,Working,Group,The,Vibration,API,enables,developers,to,trigger,the,vibration,mechanism,in,a,hosting,device,such,as,a,smartphone,The,vibration,length,and,pattern,of,the,vibrations,can,be,customized,The,API,offers,simple,tactile,feedback,not,fine,grained,control,The,API,should,not,be,confused,with,sending,alerts,and,notifications,as,the,Notifications,API,can,handle,these,requests,The,Vibration,API,does,not,specify,wether,or,not,the,hosting,device,contains,a,vibration,mechanism